{"tid":774004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 工作壓力爆煲　男子車廂自製毒氣室尋死","createTime":"2018-08-10T03:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T04:48:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3edea1eedf1d24a072b868a52a1666b7601b7c72","tid":774004,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:49:42.000Z","msg":"今日(10日)早上7時許，秀茂坪寶達邨多層停車場，有保安員巡邏期間發現一輛本田私家車引擎開動一段時間，唯私家車未有離去，保安上前查看，赫見一名男子躺臥在司機位上，而車尾死氣喉接駁一條膠管直入車廂，疑有人自製毒氣室自殺。保安員敲打車窗但男子已沒有反應，大驚下立即報警，消防及救護員趕至，將昏迷司機救出送院搶救。<br />\n<br />\n警員在場調查，證實尋死姓何(43歲)男子亦為車主，報住在秀茂坪邨，警員在車上發現一張疑似遺書的字條，內容寫上「原諒我的軟弱 十分累了 愛你們的每個」，稍後聯絡事主親友了解。據悉，有人近日因<span style=\"color: red;\">工作問題不開心</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180810/bkn-20180810073701929-0810_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180810%2Fbkn-20180810073701929-0810_00822_001.html&d=58LXFaom6tC%2FuxYJ5NNIDl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=bbbc6ac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180810/bkn-20180810073701929-0810_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"87f79c22a6e4ab51ced05fc0e1672431f52957d7","tid":774004,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:50:00.000Z","msg":"工作問題不開心<br />\n工作問題不開心<br />\n工作問題不開心"},{"pid":"0072431b20a21c0002f77440e525710085d15d61","tid":774004,"uid":34562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f79c22a6e4ab51ced05fc0e1672431f52957d7","tid":774004,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:50:00.000Z","msg":"工作問題不開心<br />\n工作問題不開心<br />\n工作問題不開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"肯定又係it狗"},{"pid":"b0cb497fc71abd72ff510c2159b36ae6b960a0ee","tid":774004,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14043a07bd99433598a2ba6842146cf36f6e109c","tid